{"tid":2032233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日唔會有和勇之分 只有香港人","createTime":"2020-05-24T03:01:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T03:59:32.000Z","uid":151061,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f9cd8e35062f8da2be229881b99c28a1647930e3","tid":2032233,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:01:06.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落 冇和勇之分<br />\n出得黎就唔怕被票控 但大家要幫電話叉好電<br />\n一有狀況就<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻錄影</span></span></strong> <br />\n有機會幫到自己同其他人<br />\n去之前去黃店食d野 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">拎張單keep起</span></span><br />\n根本冇送頭一詞 無論做咩都送頭<br />\n做又送唔做都送<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n從來都係香港人既革命 唯有香港獨立先做到"},{"pid":"4da6459394cb861fd231b0362ebd257a01a86f24","tid":2032233,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:06:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"268d96ce509866bbb2b4dd9c2f70c1ab985f78e2","tid":2032233,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b18673122da8ddab6397d7ca3ef5d2e1cfd87993","tid":2032233,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:08:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d0cf4bc8c6e089b61c4b8d18c861c2e3358dba86","tid":2032233,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:12:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fd4a50be487d8f8d3b51a0a619a0a2503f1ecfa3","tid":2032233,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:54:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3d30c42a4d4d881ec3a3fe3f777ceab4feee328","tid":2032233,"uid":151061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}